        <h2>About The Podcast</h2>
        <p>
          "QA Insights" is a weekly podcast where I sit down with Quality Assurance professionals, test automation experts, 
          and quality leaders to discuss testing strategies, automation frameworks, and career advancement in QA. Each episode 
          is packed with practical insights, real-world testing scenarios, and best practices from experienced QA practitioners.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you're a manual tester looking to transition into automation, a QA engineer seeking to advance your career, 
          or a quality leader building effective testing teams, this podcast offers valuable takeaways from real-world 
          experiences in Quality Assurance and software testing.
        </p>
